  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>The\n        Fire Sermon</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>The Fire Sermon was preached by the Buddha against the\n        fires of lust and other passions that destroy people and\n        prevent their regeneration.</p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"kassapaB.htm\"><i>Kassapa\n                The Fire Worshipper</i></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"matthew5-7.htm\"><i>Matthew\n                5-7, The Sermon on the Mount</i></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\"</font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
